未.definition: not yet; did not; have not; not; 8th earthly branch: 1-3 p.m., 6th solar month (7th July-6th August), year of the Sheep; ancient Chinese compass point: 210°

未亡人.definition: a widow (a widow's way of referring to herself in former times)

未來.definition: future; tomorrow; CL:個|个[ge4]; approaching; coming; pending

未來主義.definition: Futurism (artistic and social movement of the 20th century)

未來派.definition: Futurism (artistic and social movement of the 20th century)

未卜.definition: not foreseen; unpredictable; not on the cards

未卜先知.definition: predictable; sth one can predict without being a clairvoyant

未及.definition: to not have had time; to have not yet; not to touch upon

未可厚非.definition: not to be censured too strictly (idiom); not altogether inexcusable; understandable

未可同日而語.pinyin: wei4 ke3 tong2 ri4 er2 yu3
未可同日而語.definition: lit. mustn't speak of two things on the same day (idiom); not to be mentioned in the same breath; incomparable

未命名.definition: untitled; unnamed; no name; nameless; unknown name

未央.definition: (literary) not ended; not yet over; close to the end

未央區.definition: Weiyang District of Xi’an 西安市[Xi1 an1 Shi4], Shaanxi

未始.definition: not necessarily; may not turn out to be; maybe not

未料.definition: to not anticipate; to not expect; unanticipated; unexpected

未時.definition: 1-3 pm (in the system of two-hour subdivisions used in former times)

未有.definition: is not; has never been; never occurring; unprecedented

未果.definition: to fail to eventuate; (verb suffix) to be unsuccessful in ...ing

未決.definition: as yet undecided; unsolved; still outstanding

未然.definition: in advance; before it happens (cf preventative measures); forestalling

未知數.definition: unknown number; (fig.) an unknown; an uncertainty

未知數兒.definition: erhua variant of 未知數|未知数[wei4 zhi1 shu4]

未經.definition: not having undergone; without (having gone though a certain process)

未置可否.definition: to refuse to comment; same as 不置可否

未能.definition: cannot; to fail to; unable to

未能免俗.definition: unable to break the custom (idiom); bound by conventions

未艾.definition: (literary) not having come to its term

未遂.definition: to fail to accomplish; unsuccessful (attempt); abortive (coup d'état); attempted (murder, suicide); unfulfilled (wish)

未遑多讓.definition: see 不遑多讓|不遑多让[bu4 huang2 duo1 rang4]

未達一間.definition: differing only slightly; not much between them

未雨綢繆.definition: lit. before it rains, bind around with silk (idiom, from Book of Songs 詩經|诗经); fig. to plan ahead; to prepare for a rainy day
